
To build & run on linux
=======================

Install opengl libraries
------------------------
sudo apt-get install
freeglut3
freeglut3-dev
libglew1.5
libglew1.5-dev
libglu1-mesa
libglu1-mesa-dev
libgl1-mesa-glx
libgl1-mesa-dev

Make
----
browse to the balls directory
type 'make'
a 'balls' executable should be created

To build & run on mac
=====================

Make
----
browse to the balls directory
type 'make x'
a 'balls' executable should be created

